title: Riff Interactive guitar tutorial - Beginning Slide Guitar
description:
Riff Interactive guitar tutorial on Beginning Slide Guitar.

** NOTE: This is an bin package.


This needs to be burnt onto CD with Nero or use a virtual Drive to save the world from burning - I use MagicDisc.

This tutorial is fairly old technology and a bit fussy, but what the hell, it works and it's free.


*********If you don't know how to use it, should you really be on a computer?******
